             were indicted for <rs id="t18200918-264-off1512" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18200918-264-off1512" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18200918-264-off1512" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, from the person of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18200918-264-victim2471" type="victimName">
                           Henry Fielding 
                           Corfe
                        <interp inst="t18200918-264-victim2471" type="surname" value="Corfe"></interp>
